---+ About this Document
This document is an overview of the twiki pages that relate to the [[Documentation.GlossaryOfTerms#DefsComputeElement][compute element (CE)]].
This page provides links to information on how to plan, install, operate, use, and troubleshoot the CE as well as background information on how the CE operates and the software that is present on a CE. 
   * [[#Background_and_Planning][Background and Planning]]: Information on planning and understanding the CE
   * [[#Installation][Installation guides for the CE]]: Installation guides for installing the various CE components
   * [[#Operation][CE Operations]]: Information on operating and monitoring a CE
   * [[#Troubleshooting][Troubleshooting Information]]: Information on troubleshooting problems with the CE software
   * [[#References][Reference Information]]: References to get more information related to the CE

---+ Background and Planning
   * [[Documentation.Release3.SitePlanning][Site Planning Guide]]: Overall site planning information
   * [[Documentation/Release3.InstallBestPractices][Installation Best Practices]]: Information on best installation practices using YUM/RPM
   * [[Documentation.Release3.UnderstandingComputeElement][Understanding the Compute Element]]: The software and services on a CE

---+ Installation
   * [[Documentation.Release3.PreparingComputeElement][Preparing the Compute Element]]: What needs to be in place before beginning CE Installation
   * [[Documentation/Release3.InstallBestPractices][Installation Best Practices]]: Information on best installation practices using YUM/RPM
   * [[Documentation.Release3.InstallComputeElement][Installing a Globus GRAM-based Compute Element]]
   * [[Documentation.Release3.InstallHTCondorCE][Installing an HTCondor-CE-based Compute Element]]
   * [[Documentation/Release3.InstallRSV][Installing RSV Monitoring]]: Resource and Services Validation service installation
   * [[Documentation.Release3.InstallWNClient][Installing the Worker Node Client]]

---+ Operation
   * [[Documentation/Release3.ValidatingComputeElement][Validating CE functionality]]: How to verify the CE is fully functional
   * [[Documentation.Release3.FirewallInformation][Configuring the CE to work with firewalls]]: Firewall configuration for the CE (and other services)

---+ Troubleshooting
   * [[Documentation/Release3.KnownProblems][Known problems]]: Important known or common problems and their solutions
   * [[Documentation/Release3.TroubleshootingComputeElement][Troubleshooting GRAM-based CE problems]]: Information on meaning of errors and their causes
   * [[Documentation/Release3/TroubleshootingHTCondorCE][Troubleshooting HTCondor-CE]]: HTCondor-CE specific troubleshooting information
   * [[Documentation/Release3.HelpProcedure][Procedures for getting help]]

---+ References
   * [[Documentation.Release3.SitePlanning][Site Planning]]: Overall site planning information
   * [[Documentation.Release3.IniConfigurationOptions][Ini Configuration Options]]: Ini file format and options for osg-configure
   * [[Documentation.Release3.OSGServices#Compute_Element_Services][Services running on the CE]]: CE Services and their fucntions
   * [[Documentation.Release3.EnvironmentVariables][Environment Variables]]: Available environment variables and their definitions
   * [[Documentation.SiteAdminResources][Resources for Site Admins]]: List of resources available for Site Admin assistance
   * [[Documentation.SecurityRisksCE][Security risks on the CE]]

